{"tid":92001,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"講下火影入面你最鍾意嘅「情」","createTime":"2017-01-23T09:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T07:24:18.000Z","uid":13938,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74d7d947cb7975ceec40750f0249aeefc1be9a53","tid":92001,"uid":13938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:18:41.000Z","msg":"睇過火影都知 唔同人物之間 都有好多情<br />\n個人覺得火影寫嘅情 其實好高汁<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n親情：嗚人一家、佐助一家等等<br />\n友情：嗚佐、卡卡西同凱、我愛羅同嗚人等等<br />\n愛情（算較少篇幅）：嗚人、四代、再不斬等等<br />\n師徒：自來也、阿斯瑪等等<br />\n<br />\n感覺上較少漫畫做到 配角之間都有好多connection"},{"pid":"901a3df16d229c4a903ca3ec51a66ce771a7d038","tid":92001,"uid":48960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:22:06.000Z","msg":"基情"},{"pid":"7c12b87d1a1f60d002a4f684e140eabb0b366496","tid":92001,"uid":6520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:22:47.000Z","msg":"團藏同三代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"109243fc2437509b1c4e61b59457bd683907436c","tid":92001,"uid":22975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:25:17.000Z","msg":"香璘 柒助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede1b48345917e4caa28bc9c79bf967790f775a8","tid":92001,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:26:22.000Z","msg":"黏土 爆炸 迪達拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7145987c76a48598ec4841dcaf93528c03572879","tid":92001,"uid":13938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:28:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>團藏同三代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夠冷門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91661b3c7b220fef4f8b8ada4791bac57736481","tid":92001,"uid":1861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:38:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>團藏同三代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agr